-- Talisman Faces Potential Buchan Alpha Shutdown, Upstream Reports
-- B y   M e e r a   B h a t i a
-- 2011-12-30T07:47:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-30/talisman-faces-potential-buchan-alpha-shutdown-upstream-reports.html
Talisman Energy Inc. (TLM)  may face the
possible close of the Buchan Alpha facility as the U.K. Health &
Safety Executive has ordered the company to submit a revised
safety case, Upstream reported, citing documents.  Talisman said it remains “confident” that Buchan is safe
and continues to work with the HSE to successfully conclude the
matter, the Oslo-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Meera Bhatia in Oslo at 
 mbhatia2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christian Wienberg at 
 cwienberg@bloomberg.net  